RdbmsColumnImpl
public interface RdbmsColumn
extends RdbmsModelElement

A representation of the model object 'Rdbms Column'.

The following features are supported:

  • Rdbms Type
  • Rdbms Owner
  • Rdbms Key
  • Rdbms Foreign Key
